ke when we - she married my father, she was a - she was a very good singer, she was called Mary Davies a g}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2100535\charrsid2636949 r}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13726020\charrsid2636949 
anted, meaning Mary Davies the singer. She was also called Mary Davies Cwmbychan. And then when we moved over here she was called Mary Davis Broad Street, so she had a few titles.
