rge bedrooms they were too, upstairs, and three rooms downstairs with a very large - greenhouse, or what you'd call a vestibule now isn't it, very large. And we had a side entrance, we lived at the - the end house and - my elder brother was a very good mu
sician, used to take puipils, and they'd come to the side entrance into this vestibule, have lessons in this mid room that we had in this house here.
