No, my - do you know my mother and father used to do that, as I say on a Monday the shoes were cleaned ready for Sunday too and the every day shoes. Mother used to do that mostly.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5506367 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13726020\charrsid2636949 Would he make the fires, your father?
