\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7226846 GW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13726020\charrsid2636949 Yes. Yes. But it was - my moth
er would take us to bed. And - every night, and she'd say the prayers with us. And - never could understand, it was a - such an unusual prayer that she'd give - she gave us, all the children. Not gentle Jesus meek and mild Oh Lord be merciful unto me a si
