No, downstairs on the mantelpiece. Oh yes. The living room always, yes, all of us. Oh yes, that was quite a performance. And ducking apple night, and the tub in front of the fire, you know. Oh yes, oh a whale of a time duc
king apple night. And the boys at the back pushing our heads under the water of course.
