 he'd go down the moors, he was sort of the Robin Hood for widows, you see. He'd shoot a rabbit and take them to the poor widow who couldn't afford to buy a Sunday joint. And he'd take his gun down to the Margan Moors and - a sure shot. Well Stubbs was th
