y up now he said. And try the solo. And indeed my mother won the solo. And put the bag round my neck as a baby. With a prize in it. And you're ' you're - you're grandfather was so delighted he said, well there's a young lady coming up now, he said, with a
 baby}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid132301\charrsid2636949  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13726020\charrsid2636949 
in arms, he said, she's taking the place of Miss somebody in Scewan, and, he said, I'm sure, he said, we'll have a treat. And when my mother won and coming to Dyffryn of course with your father, well - well of course there was nothing the matter, and 
