ly if we were having it separately, well not separately, a few at a time, but every Sunday it was - general grace, with my father. And we'd have to respond, and we'd - all have to say thank God for our good food, at the end, we all had to say that togethe
r.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5506367 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13726020\charrsid2636949 He would say grace first would he?
