\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7226846 GW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13726020\charrsid2636949 
My mother was a - more fond of politics. I think it was because he was - then - it was only Liberal and Tory you see, and I think because - he was - well a - a - working man, and he thought it was more fitting - with his everyday life - the
 - he - and of course - all non-conformists are all Welsh people seem to be - inclined for the Liberal - you see, and Mark Bond was a big noise of course - in Carmarthen, and - I think it - that was handed down, from family to family, especially for - if 
- if it had been in a working class family you see. Very few Conservatives would be you see. And that was - well I'll not bring that story in now about Thomas Thomas chappellers you know that don't you? Don't you, don't you?
