ld see it very very tame there - and he was a Deacon, he'd sit - and I can remember this when I was a little girl - a big sort of a - where the Bible was - a big sort of a red cushion with long tassles hanging down, and Thomas Thomas would sit there behin
d
 this tassle in a chair, he was an Elder, well - so - couldn't see him very well, so he thought, I'd better go back, perhaps Edwar Matthews now - is in only - I won't go in the chapel, I'll go in the vest - I'll go in a - in the - in the lobby and see wha
