No, no, they never took part in anything. They only formed their own opinion and read the different - the different speeches and that you know and formed their own opinion, they never - they never made an outward show of it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5506367 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13726020\charrsid2636949 When your parents were not doing their work how did they spend their time?
