es, the working part of the church I tell you, if there was any socials work or any singing to be done - in the choirs or singing solo or anything, 'cos she had a - very very good voice - to the end, and - we - we were all - and the - my mother didn't lik
e us to be on the fringes of the church, we all had to be active in the church, all of us as children. She wouldn't have us on the fringes. Wel all had to - do our - our bit in the church as they did.
