ed - just went to pay, and - your grandfather was Secretary of that club. And - we'd go - we children sometimes would have to go to it, in a big room, not anything to do with bars. You'd go up a lot of stairs and it was a very very big room with tables, a
nd your grandfather was a Chairman - and your grandfather then would organize these eistedfodds in the drill hall Taibach. And my mother always took part in those and always went to the eistedfodd.
