 and a shawl, what do you want an old thing like this with no teeth. But do you know that - that affect me so much - blood is thicker than water, you see what I mean, so I said - no, no, no you can't take her, no no. And they'd been giving me - what I can
 
remember very well was the - women from the chapel, the young girls, my sister's young friends, 'cos she was only sixteen, had come up from chapel to see the baby on the Sunday morning. And - do you remember - Easter Banks? She had come up and all the gir
