ver - never did, I had a lot of patience. Patience with customers because - Blod - and Idris would say, oh look, some awful tabs, we called them tabs, look who's coming}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4272343\charrsid2636949  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
