\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7226846 GW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13726020\charrsid2636949 Idris. Idris. That's right. And - my elder brother -
 Dai the same - now - during that week, during the first week - that Idris was taken with peritonitis and - the elder brother. We lost the younger brother a year before that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5506367 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13726020\charrsid2636949 That was not long after you were married was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7226846 GW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13726020\charrsid2636949 That was the same yea
r we lost my younger brother, twenty-four we lost my young brother. And - Dai died the following year. And Idris was critically ill, he'd taken him an x}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4613522\charrsid2636949 -}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid13726020\charrsid2636949 ray, he was so scared - to see his cond}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4613522\charrsid2636949 ition and his result from the x-}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13726020\charrsid2636949 
ray. The specialist at - and it 
shocked him, and he was for four months there were no hopes for him in Aberavon hospital and Dai died in the cottage hospital. I had to carry on in the business, couldn't show him - couldn't sign a cheque or anything to - months afterwards, we weren't all
owed to give him any worry or trouble at all.
