Yes, it broadened - it broadened my mind to - other - other things you know, into other company, and - different types of people. You met so many different t}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4613522\charrsid2636949 y}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid13726020\charrsid2636949 pes some very fidgety, some very easy to get on with you know in business, you know them}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4613522\charrsid2636949  coming }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
