\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7226846 GW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13726020\charrsid2636949 Oh yes. As I tell you, singing, choirs, everything like that. Drama, We}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid540512\charrsid2636949 l}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13726020\charrsid2636949 sh drama. Drama in the church, we used to have lots of little plays, Welsh plays in the church, and - English plays too of course. And - the operatic society, oh - always ful
l of - full of - activities. Anything like that.
