\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7226846 GW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13726020\charrsid2636949 You mean - before I was married? Be - be -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5506367 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13726020\charrsid2636949 This is the period after you left school and you were in the shop.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7226846 GW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13726020\charrsid2636949 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5506367 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13726020\charrsid2636949 What did you do in the evening then?
