Oh join these various choirs and - the different - the operatic society and the - drama, all these - all these different societies. The Welsh Society, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5506367 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13726020\charrsid2636949 What did you do there?
