Oh in these various - activities you see, the choirs, the - the - the drama, and - in the shop particularly of course there were - no end of - y
oung men there who were interested in all sorts of - politics discussions and all sorts of things, and of course boy friends, we'd go out with boy friends of course. Oh we had a whale of a time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5506367 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13726020\charrsid2636949 Did you ever bring them home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7226846 GW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13726020\charrsid2636949 Yes, mother always e
