Millie Hopcyn}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13726020\charrsid2636949 .
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7226846 GW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13726020\charrsid2636949 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5506367 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13726020\charrsid2636949 She was your special friend?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7226846 GW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13726020\charrsid2636949 Special friend.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5506367 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13726020\charrsid2636949 And any special boy friend?
