 was a music - a very good musician bringing some boys on a Thursday afternoon, they were playing in the night at that time, musical director and he'd bring some of the boys of the band with}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11236177\charrsid2636949  
}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13726020\charrsid2636949 him on the afternoon, because my brother being in the business hal
f day on Thursday, they'd come here and I'd made a lovely black satin cushion, with velvet flow - with violets, purple violets now, and green, for a wedding. And would you believe it, my husband went to sit on the chair and I had it up on an easel you see
, against this chair. My husband went and sat right on it before it had dried until he - his suit was all violets and my cushion was ruined.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5506367 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13726020\charrsid2636949 What did you actually have to do, you used to paint the violets?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7226846 GW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13726020\charrsid2636949 Yes, the paint - was pen - pen painted.
 With - Windsor and Newton's oil paints of course, and - pictures we were very fond of make - oil painting pictures, but at that time pen painting was a very very - fashionable way of painting you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5506367 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13726020\charrsid2636949 Did your parents expect to know where you were?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7226846 GW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13726020\charrsid2636949 
Oh yes. We had to give an account of ourselves always. And we always did. We'd always - they'd always encourage us to discuss - who we'd been with and where, and that sort of thing, and what type of people they were.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5506367 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13726020\charrsid2636949 Did you have to be home by a certain time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7226846 GW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13726020\charrsid2636949 
Oh yes. Oh yes, ten o'clock. And if we weren't there was a - we were - drawn over the colas you see, and our boyfriends if they come to the house had to go by ten. Half past nine to ten always, or my father'd be shouting - go to bed at 
half past nine - shout over the banisters, it's high time those young boys went home. You see. Very very strict that way.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5506367 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13726020\charrsid2636949 What age were you when you married?
