\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5506367 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13726020\charrsid2636949 How long had you known your husband?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7226846 GW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13726020\charrsid2636949 Oh I knew him from - I was engaged at twenty-one - I knew him - oh - knew him - years before that, although I didn't go seriou}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11236177\charrsid2636949 s}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13726020\charrsid2636949 
ly because - my father being dead against cinemas and theatres you see it was a - oh it was terrible - we - we'd gone on the sly for a twelve m
onth, because - he was so dead on - on these things, he couldn't stand anything - any cinemas or theatres, they were the work of the devil he reckoned you see. Of course my mother had a broader outlook entirely, and he got to hear now that I was courting 
this musician. He thought it was terrible thing that - Gwen was going with a showman, what was this - said that you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5506367 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13726020\charrsid2636949 How did you manage to court him on the sly?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7226846 GW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13726020\charrsid2636949 Oh - he wasn't quite as observant as my mother you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5506367 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13726020\charrsid2636949 But your mother knew?
