Oh - oh yes. Oh around - this - really the next street in George Street. With a - with two old maids, Miss Bendles, and they always fussed over him you know. They - they were very very kind to him, these two old maids.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5506367 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13726020\charrsid2636949 He didn't actually go back to Nottingham at all?
