i
g job up in Nottingham and he was a bit of a fraud, but of course you get frauds in every nationality, but because he was Welsh all Welsh were frauds, of course, you see. So - she - Alice now this elder sister, who I was very fond of, he had three sisters
 - sent me some beautiful Nottingham lace back with Wally when they came back - from the holiday. And I sent a latter back to thank her very much for the lace of course. She sent - and - later on}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
