down. The others didn't feel very much - they knew my brother was very ill, they didn't think - but she came down, the elder sister, this one I said was a very good singer and conductress. His father and mother didn't feel like coming down, my father and 
m
other - my mother didn't go, because she was nursing my brother of course. She didn't go at all, she couldn't go. She was nursing my brother. And then it was - all the brothers and sisters, cousins, and friends, very close friends who'd been very kind and
 helped us with the - making o}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16669188\charrsid2636949 f different things of the trousers}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13726020\charrsid2636949  and that before we went you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5506367 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13726020\charrsid2636949 How did you decide who to invite?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7226846 GW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13726020\charrsid2636949 Well - as I tell you we would have had it much more fussy but for my brother but - afterwards then we - to please 
everybody we had different days for the different parties of my father's relatives and our relatives, and - if they could have come from Nottingham, but I tell you only his sister came down.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5506367 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13726020\charrsid2636949 How were - people invited?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7226846 GW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13726020\charrsid2636949 Oh - by letter. By letter then, we didn't have the cards or invitations then as it is now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5506367 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13726020\charrsid2636949 By word of mouth at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7226846 GW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13726020\charrsid2636949 Oh yes, friends around word of mouth, and neighbours.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5506367 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13726020\charrsid2636949 Did any have to stay overnight?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7226846 GW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13726020\charrsid2636949 No, we didn't have the room, but they stayed with my sister
 and - and - my brother, and - Liz - Liz - and - Idris - Idris was married then, stayed with him. And some stayed in the Grand Hotel.
