Well - strangely enough it's the - it's the parents of the bride that paid - now - they tell me that the bridegroom's supposed to pay for the flowers but we never - never did in our days, it was the brid}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid16669188\charrsid2636949 e}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13726020\charrsid2636949 's - family that paid for all th
