\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7226846 GW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13726020\charrsid2636949 There was a - there were two men that we knew, they were - they used to make th
e tea for us in the operatic society, as I tell you the operatic society were there with these paper streamers. They made an archway for us to pass through you see. And - these two men had a rope, we - Wally had to pay money to them of course, the bridg}{
