e was an expert at floral decorations, oh - her bouquets and her wreathes - it - it - she was a really - a first class - florist, and she presented me with oh - it was a - a huge sheaf of white - not the arum, the Easter lily you know, the lovely lily. An
d
 I've got a photograph here of - the - and - I remember my brother in the bedroom, he was very artistic, wanted me dressed and to see me before I went, and I had to hold this a special way, I wasn't holding it correctly, 'cos he was very artistic, and he 
