y were terrors some of them. They'd say most terrible things to you. And you had to put up with it with a grin of course, and - it wouldn't do to show you were annoyed you see, that's just what they wanted, and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5506367 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13726020\charrsid2636949 You didn't go back to work after you were married did you?
